[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering path contexts**\n\nI'm trying to figure out the best way to manage paths. It seems like when I'm working from a worktree, I may not have a clear source context. So, my best guess is to use absolute paths when referencing things outside my current worktree. It feels more straightforward that way, avoiding potential confusion with relative paths. I'll make sure to stick with absolute paths to keep things clear and well-structured.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0b06730402872aed0169f615c14afc819ea45d8cc4da2eef29\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp9hXEOWvqq36XamyH7OKJ-HYsexcq0djT6M4RtDGdbVWLP5Do5sDYCpQmxTKqvUg813UJHYQjU7ZwWSkLo339AjkMSmmI3uyAR2qbc1QhcL6LYIijZ7Pl0bAmtmk0sFBub1DyiTZnSFdaId0NrXHZp_mMx6PrEAJVNU1WYdkU7MyRsVj9tg1c7uHRC3iHu3dP9Uob7EzkxHBYdw-vUwbJvlanXgk5fyzoNNYEGIWguV1euQR8lBkkl3Jt8msGqY-k-zff8an4YqVkPcnMbfgqFT32EY8ZLp4rvdehF1FZPQ2i7fM94hkfRcTq5a934dMm7mpz-4b8D5ugXdvXhGVPyXDc4nOZsPx5I_YyGFNvdMAFRGs9g-OXbpRvrWAn6wouNhHudNe1GCEdW9uTiQrQruy94NWJaupyWhqoivnDxyIn8gzPfw4EOvgd5kwoPw3XdLNwOPB4-7iem3pEspOArytlsLrUv2N4_w5QUA0v5Hw5XEJi6zV8uSlJrrwNlD5t04z4B1Vd8BoRZ5LL3MdWQuPaEnsZWdRsoAgQXgIIxRX_3u6H3bJlWg_r8wZX9419JQ3VPn1L32bDaDDDLBDHkEFr42qwByMS59wbXSM7KegwOieFsrVS26OuqbCz7FSZPaBxvHVUp5wdjVbH8-vRkaTpA1orq6TScMNy7x2ozDEg0KVhs0HgYiS8kXGRnxdQCIoKm0LF5E_EVz85U9vSlqlBG2X2AGgQS8i2rS0-QCvazLuK8toL722TRd4vKwJPvRkMp0ep8OJpC4glsEsKNeBy-SCC7ismAmPlDsSv8KdWRIej5rm92H9IdobdkG06pZFz1jDWu09JjIXjL_SkbjkS_RPgtQuKXSsYAH9Ch-lC356vTFeKxCG0IQkvYd7JVfz8BiyrnVxVB4yOU-J95LSVXjBHK9I_uelxArpT1FHrVoBSmCnUJRHfG-NhTDC8uWoBSGSIhRy2ov1uQL8duBLUMB1-8Tw8EpNQaOVDioqfUVNHyRvdgM7tsXsWFAvh674z0WsA5S6ATLwVvoSxol-3UQ==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering path contexts**\\n\\nI'm trying to figure out the best way to manage paths. It seems like when I'm working from a worktree, I may not have a clear source context. So, my best guess 